 Step 1: Installed Node Version Manager (nvm) using:
curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

Step 2: Closed and reopened the terminal.

Step 3: Installed Node.js version 20.16.0 using:
nvm install 20.16.0

Step 4: Installed Sass using:
npm install sass -v 3.7.4